title: EltaMD SPF 50 UV Sport Sunscreen, 7 Fluid Ounce
description: A high-powered, SPF 50 sun block ideal for outdoor athletes, EltaMD 's UV sport is a durable, water resistant formula that won't wear off or run. This incredible formula brings you long-lasting UVA and UVB protection with a unique blend of effective, active ingredient, including z-cote, a form of micronized zinc oxide. The moisturizing lotion formula leaves the skin feeling soft with no greasy residue. Great for athletes and children.
